{"tid":1437824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「SuperM」團名嚇壞外國粉絲！　網友驚呆：怎麼是嘉明","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:53:36.000Z","uid":213300,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0c59a460f61cab99ed9a9efbb552cb4e88002290","tid":1437824,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"記者吳睿慈／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓經紀公司三大龍頭之一SM娛樂，近年來不斷推出團體分隊，一次又一次炒熱市場話題<br />\n。日前再出新招，網羅SHINee泰民、EXO伯賢、Kai以及NCT Lucas、TEN、泰容、Mark，組<br />\n成「超級男團」SuperM，將積極開拓美國市場。<br />\n<br />\n經紀公司創辦人李秀滿美國時間7日在洛杉磯舉辦記者會，證實由7位成員組成的「SuperM<br />\n」男團，預計在10月出道，且將積極拓展美國市場，因此出道地點也設在該地，李秀滿稱<br />\n呼他們是「KPOP復仇者聯盟」，未來將會以正式的團體名義，推出專輯以及回歸。<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，掀起一陣正反評論，卻也有海外粉絲質疑「團名非常不適合」，若沒有看仔<br />\n細團名，容易將「SuperM」看成「sperm」，英文意指精液，令許多英文圈的歌迷驚呆直<br />\n呼「確定他們有想要待在一個名叫『精液』的團體嗎？」、「可不可以有更好的團名」，<br />\n大批粉絲掀起改名要求，希望SM有聽到他們的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，SM大舉推出團體「SuperM」，在粉絲眼中不太看好，他們擔心天團等級的EXO十<br />\n月在日本將舉辦巡迴演唱會，擔心伯賢、Kai的體力無法負荷之外，泰民還有許多個人活<br />\n動要兼顧，沒辦法好好休息，NCT目前也還沒在南韓站穩腳步，如果要抽出成員到美國活<br />\n動，粉絲也擔心會影響團體聲勢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1509669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1509669&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=f2f8b0ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1509669</a>"},{"pid":"f23d7cc09b27e58a6ad6f9161ba8d16f083e736a","tid":1437824,"uid":213300,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"sperm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22f363fcaa5d5ad79d782de625383001ff813dd","tid":1437824,"uid":143093,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母黃旭熙 咪撚搞鳩我泰民伯賢kaikai"},{"pid":"84eb27f3f78f2ab4c0301b29dff754e037da3c90","tid":1437824,"uid":44243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"買專輯送精液 好快衝上billboard"},{"pid":"3ae6a232f43f6031b5dba3750698bd99ab89737c","tid":1437824,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c22f363fcaa5d5ad79d782de625383001ff813dd","tid":1437824,"uid":143093,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母黃旭熙 咪撚搞鳩我泰民伯賢kaikai"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"唔屌牙mark?"},{"pid":"df976b9c14be4c821665ebdf48fe9c902b87554b","tid":1437824,"uid":70274,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"岩牙 呢間公司既偽人本身就系毒撚先會追 日常既作用就系要來打j"},{"pid":"55f7c2bddd620b07d0f5a56c3bfc4f04f4670a3d","tid":1437824,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df976b9c14be4c821665ebdf48fe9c902b87554b","tid":1437824,"uid":70274,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"岩牙 呢間公司既偽人本身就系毒撚先會追 日常既作用就系要來打j"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaa98697a410a7f4d6520917ccc2f4ebcf3ece9","tid":1437824,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"sperm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas